  "*** THIS SHOULD BREAK THE CURSE OF THE DEAD WATERS ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** この呪いを打ち破るのだ！死の水域の呪いを！ ***",
