  },
  "*** BUT WITHOUT IT THE BAY IS NOW ALMOST EMPTY ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** しかしそれなしでは、湾は今やほとんど空っぽだ ***",
