  "*** YOU HAVE 20 SECONDS TO REACH AND DEFEND THE TOP OF THE TOWER ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** 20秒以内に塔の頂上に到達し、防衛してください ***",
