  "*** THIS CANON BLOCK THE PATH ! LET'S TRY TO REACH THIS FLOATING ISLAND ! ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** この正史のブロックが道を塞いでいる！浮遊島を目指そう！ ***",
