  "*** THIS IS THE WHOMP KING ! ITS ONLY WEAKNESS IS IN ITS BACK ! ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** ここは、ウォーンプキングのいる場所だ！ 弱点は背中だけだ！ ***",
