  },
  "*** IT'S SO BIG THAT IT WILL SHAKE THE WORLD EACH TIME IT JUMPS ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** とても大きいので、ジャンプするたびに世界を揺らすだろう ***",
