  "*** GET READY, YOU ONLY HAVE 20 SECONDS TO CLIMB THE STAIRS ! ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "さあ、準備！階段を登る時間はわずか20秒です！",
